    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the available factor evidence and determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support use of the CFD model for hemolysis prediction under VAD conditions. Factors with achieved levels below required levels are noted as areas for continued improvement in subsequent model iterations. The team considers the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the direct QoI alignment sufficient to underpin an Accepted decision at this stage of product development.",
